ACADEMIC PROJECT NOTICE

This repository contains work produced for the Agentic Business Platform (ABP)
capstone module at SKK GSB (Sungkyunkwan University Graduate School of
Business), 2026 cohort. The "KSMC" brand, business narrative, and customer
data schemas are fictional and used solely for educational and demonstration
purposes. They are not intended for commercial deployment and should not be
represented as belonging to any real Korean semiconductor manufacturer.

Reuse of the code (HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Apps Script, n8n workflow JSON) is
freely permitted under MIT terms. Reuse of the KSMC brand identity, business
case narrative, or any text content invoking the fictional KSMC entity is
restricted and requires explicit permission from the author.
